    		    =-=-=- Cavalier -=-=-=

	The Cavalier is a non spell caster who follows a strict
code of ethics and conduct. Cavaliers serve a Lord, Noble, or
King of some kind; their goal in life being to uphold chivalry.
Cavaliers would rather face death than be dishonored. The
essential hero or heroine, the Cavalier is the one who charges
off on a gleaming white horse, pennant streaming, to rescue
the innocent from the clutches of death.

Type:   Noble Warrior
Skills: Combat, Riding, Grooming
Spells: None
Prime Attributes: Dex, Str, Con

Examples: A Medieval Knight
Comments: Skilled at riding chargers and and with lance weapons,
	the Cavalier is the only guild to recieve mounts.

